Name: treatment of Cu-based antifouling paint emissions | antifouling paint emissions | EN15804GD, U
Category: A:Agriculture, forestry and fishing/03:Fishing and aquaculture/031:Fishing/0311:Marine fishing
Description: Two samples of common antifouling paints used in Peru, were analysed by the French laboratory UT2A (http://www.univ-pau.fr/ut2a) in 2010. Values are means from the two analyses, and uncertainty data are also based on measured values.
